	voiceHeading={`Bible verses for men: the Father's voice`}
	voiceIntroHtml={`Nine Bible verses for men in the Father's Heart Bible™ — each one a word from your perfect Father, straight to the weight you're carrying. Tap any reference to read and listen free.`}
	verses={[
