		{ heading: `Rest for the weight you carry`, bodyHtml: `You don't have to keep holding it all up: <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/matthew/11" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">come to your Father weary</a> and let Him give you the rest you've been running without.` },
		{ heading: `Strength that won't run out`, bodyHtml: `When you're depleted, you don't have to grit harder. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/40" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Wait on your Father</a> and He renews your strength — to run and not grow weary.` },
		{ heading: `Sonship instead of fear`, bodyHtml: `You're not a slave earning your keep. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/romans/8" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">You received the Spirit of sonship</a> — the right to call God Abba, Father, and belong as family.` },
		{ heading: `Courage you don't muster alone`, bodyHtml: `Be strong and courageous — not because you've got it handled, but because <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/joshua/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father is with you</a> wherever you go.` },
