	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a boss to satisfy`, bodyHtml: `Most of life trains a man to keep performing for approval. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. So instead of one more standard to meet, you meet the One who already calls you His son.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen on the commute, at the gym, or in the quiet before everyone wakes up. The Father's voice fits right into a man's real day.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to the weight you carry silently`, bodyHtml: `Tired? Isolated? Wondering if you're enough? Start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or learn to talk to Him with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you right where you are, without the front.` },
